creator: Feburas Games
descriptionHtml:
Solve puzzles to reconnect the electricity cables and power up the spaceship.

Features:
• 200 puzzles to solve!
• Puzzle sizes from 4x4 to 12x12 for different difficulties!
• Daily challenges with randomly selected puzzles each day!
• Hints for when you get stuck!

Challenge your brain with solving these puzzles today!
descriptionShort: Repair the spaceship to save your crew!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Rewarded hints from weekly challenge are displayed correctly;
- Clarified that the video for an extra hint is an ad.
